	(28, '锤子密谈 ，他们都谈了什么？', 2, '&lt;fieldset style=&quot;border: 0px; margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 1.4em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 3em; line-height: 1em; font-weight: bolder; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;“&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;display: inline-block; color: rgb(42, 52, 58); font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.2; vertical-align: middle; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;锤子密谈&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;display: inline-block; font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.2; vertical-align: middle; font-family: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;他们都谈了什么？&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 3em; line-height: 1em; font-weight: bolder; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/fieldset&gt;&lt;fieldset style=&quot;max-width: 100%; margin: 0.8em 1em; color: white; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;padding: 10px; border: 2px dotted white; border-top-left-radius: 8px 64px; border-top-right-radius: 48px 8px; border-bottom-right-radius: 8px 16px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px 48px; box-shadow: rgb(225, 225, 225) 8px 8px 3px; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(95, 156, 239);&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;平安夜，锤子科技在 751D·Park 的雕刻时光举办了一场线下沙龙。两位 UI 设计总监、工业设计副总裁李剑叶和 CTO 钱晨在活动上分享了 Smartisan T1 的部分细节和对各自领域的思考。&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/fieldset&gt;&lt;fieldset style=&quot;border: 0px; margin: 0.5em 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;height: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;height: 100%; width: 24px; float: left; border-top-width: 6px; border-top-style: solid; border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;height: 100%; width: 24px; float: right; border-top-width: 6px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-width: 6px; border-right-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;display: inline-block; color: transparent; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin: -13px 3px; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 202, 0); border-top-left-radius: 6px; border-top-right-radius: 6px; border-bottom-right-radius: 6px; border-bottom-left-radius: 6px; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 锤子科技的 UI 设计总监方迟说在 Smartisan OS 上有很多看不到的设计细节，就拿便签应用中的“新建”按钮举例，其实这个小 iCon 是用黄金比例固定长宽比，并用黄金螺旋确定当中的文字大小后才绘制出来的。简单来说，很多你看不到的设计，其实都和最本源的设计思路有关。&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;肖鹏曾就职百度，现任锤子科技 UI 设计总监。2012 年 4 月收到罗永浩微博发来的私信时，他还不清楚“老罗”是谁。和老罗、徐寒吃了顿饭，他便加入了锤子科技。&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;刚入职，肖鹏就开始画九宫格，虽然枯燥，但他认同老罗的部分产品设计思路。“我之前在的部门其实是用来对抗 360 的”——肖鹏说完这句，台下人都笑了。&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;锤子科技产品总监朱萧木接着在台上调侃老罗，“他很多提出的 idea 都是在厕所里想出来的”。&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;height: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;height: 100%; width: 24px; float: left; border-bottom-width: 6px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;height: 100%; width: 24px; float: right; border-bottom-width: 6px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-right-width: 6px; border-right-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/fieldset&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, '1419499521', '1419499552'),
	(29, '传富士康将为苹果生产iPhone蓝宝石屏幕', 2, '&lt;fieldset style=&quot;border: 0px; text-align: center; margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: inline-block; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-top-left-radius: 0.5em; border-top-right-radius: 0.5em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.5em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.5em; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 0.2em 0.2em 0.1em; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;传富士康将为苹果生产&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;i&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;Phone蓝宝石屏幕&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/fieldset&gt;&lt;fieldset style=&quot;width: 100%; border: none; margin: 0.5em 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;width: 40px; height: 40px; float: right; background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245); box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;width: 1px; box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) -1px 1px 2px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;border-width: 20px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(153, 153, 153) rgb(153, 153, 153); box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin-top: -38px; margin-left: 1px; border-width: 18px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(255, 255, 240) rgb(255, 255, 240); box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;width: 80%; height: 40px; line-height: 1.5em; border-bottom-width: 5px; border-bottom-style: solid; margin-left: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(42, 52, 58); border-color: rgb(166, 91, 203);&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;width: 100%; height: 100%; margin-top: 0.5em; padding: 8px; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(42, 52, 58); box-sizing: border-box;&quot; class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 由于良品率和成本等方面的问题，苹果并未在iPhone 6上采用蓝宝石显示屏，不过其并未“死心”。消息人士透露，富士康将为苹果生产用于iPhone的蓝宝石屏幕。　虽然富士康没有任何生产人造蓝宝石的经验，但该公司却对这种材料很感兴趣。过去几年中，富士康一直在积极申请各种蓝宝石相关的专利。目前，其拥有的蓝宝石专利包括配备蓝宝石的LCD屏幕、保护性蓝宝石屏幕、蓝宝石培养方法以及激光切割蓝宝石材料等。&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;　　为了满足iPhone的显示屏供应需求，苹果需要3000个165公斤的蓝宝石生产熔炉，或200个262公斤的生产熔炉。消息称，富士康已经购买了大量蓝宝石种植熔炉，准备扩充蓝宝石供应链。&lt;br class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/Upload/org/2014_12_26/525FAB9BFA5E9CD6087544FA3B0ED030/activity/549cbf347fbc4.jpg&quot; title=&quot;549cbf347fbc4.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;iPhone蓝宝石屏幕.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;　　如果苹果希望在下一代iPhone上采用蓝宝石屏幕，那么就必须在明年春季之前部署好生产熔炉。好消息是，除了富士康，来自中国和亚利桑那州的Mesa工厂也将为苹果提供蓝宝石材料，而韩国的Hansol Technics和中国哈尔滨的极光光电科技公司同样会生产蓝宝石材料屏幕。&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/fieldset&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, '1419558717', '1419558764'),
	(31, '宝宝类产品纳入准备金监管：收益率面临下降', 2, '&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;记者12月28日获悉，央行在近日下发文件，将原属于同业存款项下的存款纳入各项存款范围，其中包括证券类及交易结算类存款、银行业非存款类存放等。这意味着货币基金等宝宝类产品的同业存款今后将要缴纳存款准备金。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　不过，这并不意味着宝宝们的收益将立刻下降，因为文件同时规定上述计入存款准备金的存款适用的存款准备金率暂时为零，货币基金存款暂时先不需要缴纳准备金。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　截至昨日，央行方面未对此消息作出回应。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　&lt;strong&gt;存款基数范围扩大&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　央行规定，2015年起，央行将部分原在同业往来项下的存款纳入各项存款范围，包括证券交易结算类存放、银行非存款类存放等。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　国泰君安表示，存贷比计算口径大幅放松，存款基数范围显著扩大。部分银行同业存放、单位和个人证券交易结算金也纳入存贷比的存款计算口径，分母范围大幅拓宽，变相放松和弱化存贷比约束，尤其对存贷比较高的股份制银行、城商和农商等中小银行，监管放松影响更为明显。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　据海通证研报测算，央行调整存贷款统计口径后，商业银行存贷比平均降幅将在5%。此举意味着可释放约5.5万亿信贷额度空间，增强商业银行的信贷投放能力。而这也是国务院决定增加存贷比弹性的根本目的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;不过，昨天有业内人士对记者表示，银监会未发文调整存贷比口径予以追认。尽管多数情况下，银监会存贷比的分母与央行“各项存款”是吻合的，但并不意味着完全一致。银监会是否会调整，调整范围是否一致，现在都还不确定。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　&lt;strong&gt;宝宝类收益面临下降&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　今年3月和5月，央行调统司司长盛松成两次撰文表示，货币市场基金等同业存款应该缴存准备金。据测算，如果银行吸收的货币市场基金协议存款受存款准备金管理，银行这部分资金成本将明显增加，并将直接导致&lt;a class=&quot;wt_article_link&quot; href=&quot;http://weibo.com/57195188?zw=tech&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(4, 84, 167); text-decoration: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(4, 84, 167);&quot;&gt;余额宝&lt;/a&gt;收益的下降。假定余额宝投资银行协议存款的款项缴存20%的准备金，余额宝的年收益率将下降约1个百分点。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　借助年末资金紧张行情，宝宝类产品收益率从12月以来逐步攀升。以余额宝为例，其收益率12月1日时在4%边缘，12月27日已涨至4.852%，零钱宝、钱袋子、理财通等近10只宝宝产品收益率也涨破5%。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft Yahei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Luxi Sans&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;DejaVu Sans&amp;#39;, Tahoma, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;　　一位货币基金经理对记者表示，央行目前规定的存款准备金率是零，不过未来政策随时可能调整，对货币基金的流动性管理带来一定难度。另一位基金公司的固定收益类产品经理表示，为了存款考核，银行对于余额宝等资金量大的货币基金，可能会需求更大。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, '1419841369', '1419841613'),
